---
import PhotoCircle from "./PhotoCircle.astro";
---

<section id="methodology" class="methodology-section">
  <div class="methodology-inner">
    <div class="methodology-card">
      <div class="methodology-layout">
        <div class="methodology-photo">
          <PhotoCircle />
        </div>
        <div class="methodology-body">
          <p class="methodology-eyebrow">Proven methodology inside</p>
          <h3>At the core of Vedana lies Minimal Modeling</h3>
          <p class="methodology-text">
            <a
              href="https://minimalmodeling.com/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noreferrer"
              class="methodology-link">Minimal Modeling</a
            >
            {" "}— a methodology developed by Alexey Makhotkin, author of the
            {" "}<a
              href="https://databasedesignbook.com/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noreferrer"
              class="methodology-link">Database Design Book</a
            >.
          </p>
          <p class="methodology-text2">
            This foundation ensures that our Semantic RAG system combines:
          </p>
          <ul class="methodology-bullets">
            <li>
              <span class="bullet-amber"></span>
              <span
                ><strong>AI flexibility</strong> — LLMs that can reason, not just
                guess.</span
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="bullet-amber"></span>
              <span
                ><strong>Enterprise-grade data discipline</strong> — structured, auditable,
                and transparent.</span
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="methodology-text3">
            With Vedana, you're not experimenting on a hunch. You're building on
            a clear, proven modeling approach that was designed to handle
            real-world business complexity.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .methodology-section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }
  .methodology-inner {
    max-width: 72rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }
  .methodology-card {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid #fde68a;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #fffbeb, #fff7ed, #fff1f2);
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .methodology-card {
      padding: 2rem;
    }
  }
  .methodology-layout {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .methodology-layout {
      grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    }
  }
  .methodology-photo {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .methodology-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #b45309;
    margin: 0;
  }
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .methodology-eyebrow {
      font-size: 0.875rem;
    }
  }
  h3 {
    margin: 0.25rem 0 0;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0f172a;
  }
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    h3 {
      font-size: 1.875rem;
    }
  }
  .methodology-text {
    margin: 0.75rem 0 0;
    color: #1e293b;
  }
  .methodology-text2 {
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
    color: #334155;
  }
  .methodology-text3 {
    margin: 0.75rem 0 0;
    color: #334155;
  }
  .methodology-link {
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: #f59e0b;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
    color: inherit;
  }
  .methodology-link:hover {
    color: #b45309;
  }
  .methodology-bullets {
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }
  .methodology-bullets li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    color: #1e293b;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .bullet-amber {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 0.375rem;
    height: 0.5rem;
    width: 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    background: #d97706;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
</style>
